== Kwakira ==
Iyi filime yerekanwe na Suns Cinema, Washington DC ku bufatanye n’umuco ku ya 16 Ukwakira 2018. <ref>https://m.bpt.me/event/3606952</ref> Yerekanwe kandi mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sembène ku ya 25 Werurwe 2019. <ref>https://www.alphabetcity.org/events/sembene-film-festival-burkinabe-rising/</ref>

Iyi filime yahawe igihembo ''cyiza cyaBest Documentary Film'' kandi ihabwa igihembo cy’amanota ''meza y’umwimerere'' n’umuyobozi ''w’umugore w’indashyikirwa'' mu mujyi wa New York ku nshuro ya 7 ngarukamwaka y’imyidagaduro mpuzamahanga ya Filime (WFAIFF) mu mwaka wa 2018. <ref name="NY" />

